data.title: Asia Market Open: Bitcoin Holds Near $92k, Equities Slip On Fresh Economic Signals
data.description: Bitcoin held just under $92,000 on Friday as traders weighed a heavy mix of labour data, central bank bets and choppy equity markets in Asia, Europe and the US.Akshat Siddhant, lead quant analyst at Mudrex, said the crypto market continues to display strong resilience. “Renewed whale accumulation is supporting the ...
